Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:21:01.66,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}無数のStory　導き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:09.37,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}飛べない天使　曇り空を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:16.17,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}「僕の心の色だ…」と言う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:23.72,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}傷ついた羽根　癒してからでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:31.52,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}飛び立てばいい…なんて口ずさんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:36.19,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}傷だらけの天使たちから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:40.11,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}「your melody is love song.」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.62,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}白く吐く息が雪のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:45.58,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}「in silence.」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:47.54,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}目を閉じる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:51.00,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}曇りガラスには描けない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:54.88,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}涙で描くから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:58.38,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}僕は「ここ」で待ち続けると
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:04.89,injp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}不器用に微笑む
